Name: GSconfig_DID
Description:
Vendor Extension for OutBack Radian Series 
Split Phase Inverter Configuration Block

Name:
GSconfig_Charger_Operating
_Mode
Description:
0=All Inverter Charging Disabled, 1=Bulk 
and Float Charging Enabled

Name: GSconfig_Grid_Input_Mode
Description:
Grid Input Mode: 0=Generator, 1=Support, 
2=Grid Tied, 3=UPS, 4=Backup, 5=Mini Grid, 
6=Grid Zero

Name:
GSconfig_Grid_Lower_Input
_Voltage_Limit
Description: Grid Input AC voltage lower limit

Name:
GSconfig_Grid_Upper_Input
_Voltage_Limit
Description: Grid Input AC voltage upper limit

Name: GSconfig_Gen_Input_Mode
Description:
Grid Input Mode: 0=Generator, 1=Support, 
2=Grid Tied, 3=UPS, 4=Backup, 5=Mini Grid, 
6=Grid Zero

Name:
GSconfig_Gen_Lower_Input
_Voltage_Limit
Description: Gen Input AC voltage lower limit

Name:
GSconfig_Gen_Upper_Input
_Voltage_Limit
Description: Gen Input AC voltage upper limit

Name: GSconfig_AUX_Mode
Description:
1=Load Shed, 2=Gen Alert, 3=Fault, 4=Vent 
Fan, 5=Cool Fan, 6=DC Divert, 7=Grid 
Limit/IEEE ,8=AC Source Status,9=AC Divert
